    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465710/extras/0925b6103b1b328115585d65d5a6348f.avif?t=1747780963\" width=610 height=150 /></span><br><br><strong>【<i>主，我前来忏悔</i>。】<br>【<i>愿您宽恕我的不敬，愿您宽恕我的罪恶</i>。】</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465710/extras/6d1c4cb8709d23d7c55ea3b143099d22.avif?t=1747780963\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br><strong>丧梦</strong>——那是一种奇异的疾病。<br>一亿分之一的患病几率，百分之百的致死率。<br>丧梦病的患者无药可医，只能定期补充梦来维持生命。<br><br>主角廖沉去探视因【丧梦】住院的发小，但眼前出现的，却并非平日的医院。<br>扭曲的景象，四处游荡的怪物。<br>与发小长相一模一样的少年告诉他，<br><strong>只要找回记忆，就能离开这个恐怖的世界……</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465710/extras/e922a243263f65461b65ea55d6be11ca.avif?t=1747780963\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br>本作是一款微恐剧情向解谜游戏，含有少量血腥暴力/残酷表现，轻微bl要素。<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>剧情</strong><br>沉浸探索不可思议的黑色病院，克服对怪物和痛苦回忆的恐惧，<br>体验独一无二的少年情感与纠葛，寻求悲伤旅途的最终真相。<br></li><li><strong>美术&amp;音乐</strong><br>经典复古的像素风格地图，精美的CG与精心设计的演出。<br>在古典乐的陪伴下，沉浸于心象病院的神秘氛围。<br></li><li><strong>解谜</strong><br>难度适中的谜题，与剧情相得益彰。<br>有时也需要集中判断力，躲避四处游荡的怪物。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465710/extras/1e8b99e961e445e82e3bb359151293cd.avif?t=1747780963\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465710/extras/2b51706fdee2ba7640482e989e75a508.avif?t=1747780963\" width=300 height=189 /></span><br>饱受欺凌的唱诗班一员，将所有的梦捐献给了唯一的友人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465710/extras/4219fe3b36d6e71d4f866e71e4e0c795.avif?t=1747780963\" width=300 height=189 /></span><br>身体羸弱的“丧梦病”患者，长期住院中。对住院生活感到厌烦，希望能早日离开病院。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465710/extras/9b6058a30744ad9099c5bf45f868ea1f.avif?t=1747780963\" width=300 height=189 /></span><br>现役军官，造梦机器“玻璃房”的负责人之一。似乎正在干涉梦……？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465710/extras/800819ee5726639197aba63d0a71cb0a.avif?t=1747780963\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br><strong>「游戏时长」</strong><br>单结局通关约2小时+，全结局收集约4小时+<br><br><strong>「二周目信息」</strong><br>本作为双周目游戏，一周目结束后请从首页的【造梦】重新开始。<br><br><strong>「结局数量」</strong><br>共计六个结局（BE*3, NE*2, TE*1），其中TE需通关二周目收集。<br><br><strong>「操作方式」</strong><br>方向键进行移动<br>空格/z/Enter 确认/进行调查<br>Esc/x 取消/打开菜单<br>Shift+方向鍵 跑步<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465710/extras/c0900449063eb50503b2dce7830ee598.avif?t=1747780963\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br><strong>游戏制作/剧本：</strong>悠乙<br><strong>美术素材：</strong>啊5、栗也、栞、悠乙、百合子、Kana、阳台<br><strong>声音素材：</strong>凡凡凡Ivonne、tk/teknizer、仮之仮<br><strong>发行：</strong>梦结界工作室<br>（引用的素材来源详见游戏内ED）",
